5.body:
pragma solidity ^0.8.0; contract MyContract { unint public number1; //state variable function myFunction() public { unint num; //local variable } function newFunction() public return (uint, address) { uint num1 = 12; uint num2 = 13; number1 = num1 + num2; address myAddress = msg.sender; //global variable return (number1, myAddress); }
}
